  "title": "Ecommerce Administrative / Marketing Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Duration: 3 + 9 months=12 months Contract</p>\n<p>Location: Ubi Oxley Bizhub</p>\n<p>Working Hours: Monday – Friday 9.30am to 6.30pm, Saturday 9am-1pm</p>\n<p><em>Training Provided, 1 Year Gap Year OK</em></p>\n<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>Main Responsibilities</p>\n<p>1. Video Editing:</p>\n<p>• Video editing using Capcut for Live Stream Clips Daily on Tiktok accounts.</p>\n<p>• Video editing for products poster for Facebook/IG/Telegram</p>\n<p>2. Order Processing:</p>\n<p>• Manage E-commerce platform orders packing, coordinate deliveries, and handle returns or exchanges.( Facebook/Website/Tiktok/Shopee/Lazada)</p>\n<p>3. Customer Support:</p>\n<p>• Respond to customer inquiries via chat or email.</p>\n<p>• Assist with product recommendations and resolve issues.</p>\n<p>4. Promotions:</p>\n<p>• Set up discounts, sales, and special offers Postings on Facebook/Telegram using Canvas</p>\n<p>• Coordinate with the marketing team for campaigns.</p>\n<p>5. Inventory Management:</p>\n<p>• Track stock levels and update inventory system.</p>\n<p>6. Product Management:</p>\n<p>• Upload new products, descriptions, and pricing on the website.</p>\n<p>• Update stock levels and ensure accurate product details.</p>\n<p>7. Content Coordination:</p>\n<p>• Ensure product photos and banners are consistent and appealing.</p>\n<p>8. TikTok Live Support:</p>\n<p>• Support hosts during live events by preparing items and engaging with viewers during working hour</p>\n<p>9. • Any other additional duties or tasks assigned</p>\n<p>Key Skills</p>\n<p>• Familiarity with e-commerce platforms (e.g., Facebook/IG/Tiktok/Shopee).</p>\n<p>• Skill in Adobe Illustrator / Photoshop/ Capcut/ Canvas</p>\n<p>• Strong organizational and communication skills.</p>\n<p>• Customer service experience.</p>\n<p>• Confidence in assisting or participation in live social media events.</p>",
